                                                                            </div>
                                                                            <div class="accordion-item-description">
                                                                                <div class="description-container">
                                                                                    <p>At Alivecasino.com you can choose different types of bets. Starting with one prediction, you can use the “Single” bet option (single), with two or more predictions you can place “Express” bets, and with three or more predictions you can place a “System” or “Chain” bet. And if you would prefer to place “Single” or “System” bets, you need to select the desired option.</p>
